data.description: Discover your affordable dream home in this charming 3-bed, 2-bath sanctuary tucked away in a tranquil cove. All bedrooms & living spaces on the 1st floor for utmost convenience. Revel in neutral tones, new luxury vinyl plank flooring, and a pristine remodeled shower in primary bathroom. Kitchen boasts sleek stainless steel appliances. A fully fenced backyard, front covered patio, and rear covered patio provide ample space for outdoor relaxation. Plus, the exterior has been freshly painted.
